videos.description: Mfiondu Kabengele hits a deep 3-pointer to give Florida State a 17-14 lead over Louisville.
videos.headline: Kabengele sinks deep 3

videos.description: Louisville's Jordan Nwora drives to the basket and smashes a dunk.
videos.headline: Nwora crushes dunk in transition

videos.description: Steven Enoch scores a putback layup but receives a technical foul for yelling at some Florida State players.
videos.headline: Enoch gets technical for taunting after bucket

videos.description: Christen Cunningham finds a wide-open Jordan Nwora who capitalizes with a dunk to give Louisville a 7-point lead in a close game.
videos.headline: Nwora slam puts Louisville up 7

videos.description: M.J. Walker steals the ball and drives to the basket to tie the game late for Florida State.
videos.headline: Walker ties game with big steal and bucket

videos.description: Christen Cunningham drives to the basket, switches the ball to his left hand and makes a layup while drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Cunningham makes crossover layup and draws foul

videos.description: After battling back and forth with Louisville, Florida State wins 80-75 in overtime, picking up its fifth consecutive win.
videos.headline: FSU picks up fifth straight win in OT thriller
